						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Pramādīcha</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the gift of a pendant set with gems and precious stones by Dhaṉmarāja, nephew (<hi rend="italic">marumagaṉ</hi>) of Nallamarāja of Gappūr. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Pramādīcha (expired), Ānanda (current), Āṉi 13,</hi> are not enough for verification. The record is in late characters. </p>						

